lead_paragraph: Before Jack Sock took on 2014 U.S. Open champion Marin Cilic in the third round, the 23-year-old American acknowledged that, as of a couple of years ago, simply making it that far would have made him, to use two of his words, "satisfied" and "excited."

headline.print_headline: Sock of US Overwhelms 2014 Open Champ Cilic to Reach 4th Rd
